comments: Fournier (NYK) extends his arm into Payne's (PHX) body and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) briefly wraps and releases Robinson's (NYK) body and the contact doesn't affect his FOM.
Crowder (PHX) makes contact with Robinson's (NYK) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Quickley (NYK) briefly wraps and releases Ayton's (PHX) leg during the pick and the contact doesn't affect his FOM.
Ayton (PHX) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Barrett (NYK) that affects his driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Robinson (NYK) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  The foul is assessed to Quickley (NYK), who initiates contact with Crowder (PHX) that causes him to trip and the ensuing contact by Robinson is marginal.
Johnson (PHX) moves laterally into Barrett's (NYK) path and makes marginal contact to his body during his drive.
Quickley (NYK) wraps Ayton's (PHX) leg during the pick but the contact is marginal.
Bridges (PHX) has an arm around Barrett's (NYK) body and he initiates further body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
Crowder (PHX) briefly grasps and releases Barrett's (NYK) jersey and the contact doesn't affect his ability to rebound.
